## Deployment Checklist & Sources

- **Accessibility:** Test with screen readers (NVDA, VoiceOver) to verify skip-link and modals. Ensure aria attributes (`role="status"`) announce toasts.  
- **Security:** Use HTTPS with HSTS. Serve a strong Content Security Policy. Sanitize all inputs server-side (we use client-side escape for safety).  
- **Privacy:** As per India’s DPDP, only minimal PII (name, phone) is stored and only with consent. Use secure, HttpOnly cookies for any server tokens.  
- **Rate Limiting:** Throttle submission endpoints (leads, OTP if added) on server to prevent abuse (OWASP authentication guidance).  
- **File Uploads:** Not applicable here (no KYC on these pages), but in future ensure max sizes and scan (OWASP File Upload)【turn3search6†L0-L3】.  

